        <div class="post_details_inner">
            <h1>
                <a href="https://allthingsnuclear.org/guest-commentary/resuming-nuclear-testing-a-slap-in-the-face-to-survivors" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent Link to Resuming Nuclear Testing a Slap in the Face to Survivors">
                Resuming Nuclear Testing a Slap in the Face to Survivors                </a>
            </h1>
                            <div class="username">
                    <span class="guest-commentary">
                        Lilly Adams                         <a href="https://allthingsnuclear.org/author/guest-commentary" title="Posts by Guest Commentary" rel="author">Guest Commentary</a><!--
                        --><!--
                            --><span class='mobile-hide'>,</span><span class='mobile-hide'> UCS</span>
                                            </span><!--
                --></div>
                        <div class="post-date pipe">
                <p><span class="date">May 26, 2020</span> <span class="time">4:21 PM</span> EDT</p>
            </div>
            <div class="article-content">
                <div id="attachment_17418" style="max-width: 1510px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><a href="https://cdn.allthingsnuclear.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/radiation-warnging-signs-on-fence.jpg"><img class="size-full wp-image-17418" src="https://cdn.allthingsnuclear.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/radiation-warnging-signs-on-fence.jpg" alt="" width="1500" height="900" srcset="https://cdn.allthingsnuclear.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/radiation-warnging-signs-on-fence.jpg 1500w, https://cdn.allthingsnuclear.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/radiation-warnging-signs-on-fence-300x180.jpg 300w, https://cdn.allthingsnuclear.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/radiation-warnging-signs-on-fence-768x461.jpg 768w, https://cdn.allthingsnuclear.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/radiation-warnging-signs-on-fence-1024x614.jpg 1024w, https://cdn.allthingsnuclear.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/radiation-warnging-signs-on-fence-183x110.jpg 183w, https://cdn.allthingsnuclear.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/radiation-warnging-signs-on-fence-600x360.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text">D. Meyers/Unsplash</p></div>
<p>The <a href="https://www.washingtonpost.com/national-security/trump-administration-discussed-conducting-first-us-nuclear-test-in-decades/2020/05/22/a805c904-9c5b-11ea-b60c-3be060a4f8e1_story.html">news</a> that the Trump administration is considering resuming nuclear weapons testing is morally abhorrent. The current US moratorium on nuclear testing was put in place for many reasons, but we must not forget one crucial reason: In conducting explosive nuclear tests, the US government <a href="https://www.cdc.gov/nceh/radiation/fallout/feasibilitystudy/Technical_Vol_1_ExecutiveSummary.pdf">killed thousands of innocent people</a> and sickened untold thousands more.<br />
 <a href="https://allthingsnuclear.org/guest-commentary/resuming-nuclear-testing-a-slap-in-the-face-to-survivors" class="more-link">Read more&nbsp;&gt;</a></p>
